title: Gimme! Gimme! Gimme! (A Man After Midnight), performed by Victor Frankenstein | AAAH!BBA
description:
frankenstein was the scientist, not the monster, but also, he was totally the monster

Many years ago, Brian David Gilbert and Jonah Scott talked about how most of ABBA's music could be sung by Halloween villains. This year, they turned that 3 minute conversation into a full album.

Join my Patreon for behind the scenes stuff: https://patreon.com/briandavidgilbert
Arrangement and production by Jonah Scott: https://thealtogether.bandcamp.com/
Background vocals by Karen Han: https://twitter.com/karenyhan
